# =============================================================================
# INCLUDED FILES (Tracked by Git)
# =============================================================================
# Core automation and documentation files:
# - .vscode/                (automation scripts and VS Code configuration)
# - src/                    (Verilog source files for development examples)
# - testBench/              (custom testbenches and examples)
# - LICENSE                 (project license and commercial protection)
# - README.md               (project overview and quick start)
# - USER_GUIDE.md           (comprehensive user documentation)
# - MORE_IMPROVEMENTS.md    (future enhancement suggestions)
# - IP_PROTECTION_STRATEGY.md (intellectual property protection plan)
# - IMPLEMENTATION_SUMMARY.md (development summary)

